No. 187,

Misc.

Baumgart v. Martin, Warden. Petitioner pro se. Louis J. Lefkowitz, Attorney General of New York, Paxton Blair, Solicitor General, and Winifred C. Stanley, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Court of Appeals of New York. Certiorari denied.
